review_text:
Carol & Gene were great hosts. Loved the location! Easy walk to Harding campus & perfect place to walk!
if you need outlets for the sunroom/twinbed bring an extension cord at least 30-40' (to LR outlet)
Sunroom on carport & BR on street, but good distance from sidewalk . back yard really nice. 3 units in the house, but couldn't hear the 1 neighbor we had. I'd definitelystay there again!!
